A) Exact .config changes

Open /usr/src/linux/.config or set via menuconfig.

1️) Disable NVIDIA framebuffer
# CONFIG_FB_NVIDIA is not set

2️) Disable nouveau
# CONFIG_DRM_NOUVEAU is not set

3) Required graphics options (must be set)
CONFIG_DRM=y
CONFIG_DRM_KMS_HELPER=y
CONFIG_DRM_I915=y
CONFIG_DRM_I915_FORCE_PROBE=""
CONFIG_FB_SIMPLE=y
CONFIG_FB_EFI=y

4) Optional but recommended
CONFIG_TMPFS=y
CONFIG_DEVTMPFS=y
CONFIG_DEVTMPFS_MOUNT=y


B) Exact kernel rebuild steps (CRUX)

Run as root.

	cd /usr/src/linux
	make menuconfig
	make -j$(nproc)
	make modules_install
	make install
	reboot

C) Post-reboot verification (only commands)
lsmod | grep -E "nouveau|nvidiafb"
modprobe nvidia
nvidia-smi -> cd /usr/ports/opt && prt-get install nvidia 

D) startx
